{"type":"message","id":"37edb5d9","parentId":"8be6982a","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:29:56.365Z","message":{"role":"user","content":[{"type":"text","text":"[Fri 2026-02-27 14:29 GMT+8] [Subagent Context] You are running as a subagent (depth 1/1). Results auto-announce to your requester; do not busy-poll for status.\n\n[Subagent Task]: 【方案A：Python脚本封装】\n\n创建一个完整的Python脚本 xiaodouya_control.py，用于从WSL2控制Windows上的小豆芽应用。\n\n**已知信息：**\n- 小豆芽路径: C:\\Program Files\\xiaodouya\\新版小豆芽.exe\n- 当前运行中的进程PID: 19944 (有窗口), 还有其他子进程\n- Windows用户名: yuyirong\n- PowerShell路径: /mnt/c/Windows/System32/windowspowershell/v1.0/powershell.exe\n\n**需要实现的功能：**\n\n1. **find** - 查找所有小豆芽进程，显示PID、窗口标题、路径\n2. **activate** - 激活指定PID的窗口到前台\n3. **minimize/maximize** - 最小化/最大化窗口\n4. **list** - 列出窗口中的所有UI控件（按钮、输入框等）\n5. **click** - 点击指定坐标的控件或指定位置\n6. **type** - 在指定控件输入文本\n7. **screenshot** - 截取窗口（如果可能）\n8. **close** - 关闭应用\n\n**技术要求：**\n- 使用 PowerShell + Windows UI Automation API\n- 正确处理中文编码问题（Windows用GBK，脚本需转换）\n- 提供清晰的错误处理\n- 命令行参数使用argparse\n- 输出格式友好（支持JSON输出选项）\n\n**文件输出位置：** /home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya_control.py\n\n完成后，请简要说明实现的关键技术点和使用方法示例。"}],"timestamp":1772173796364}}
{"type":"message","id":"510ffe2f","parentId":"37edb5d9","timestamp":"2026-02-27T06:33:28.721Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"用户需要我创建一个Python脚本，用于从WSL2控制Windows上的小豆芽应用。这是一个比较复杂的任务，需要实现多个功能：\n\n1. 查找进程\n2. 激活窗口\n3. 最小化/最大化窗口\n4. 列出UI控件\n5. 点击控件\n6. 输入文本\n7. 截图\n8. 关闭应用\n\n需要使用PowerShell + Windows UI Automation API，并正确处理中文编码问题。\n\n让我开始编写这个脚本。","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"write:0","name":"write","arguments":{"path":"/home/yirongbest/.openclaw/workspace/xiaodouya_control.py","content":"#!/usr/bin/env python3\n# -*- coding: utf-8 -*-\n\"\"\"\n小豆芽应用控制器 - 从WSL2控制Windows上的小豆芽应用\n\n功能：\n- find: 查找所有小豆芽进程\n- activate: 激活窗口到前台\n- minimize/maximize: 最小化/最大化窗口\n- list: 列出UI控件\n- click: 点击控件\n- type: 输入文本\n- screenshot: 截取窗口\n- close: 关闭应用\n\n作者: OpenClaw Agent\n\"\"\"\n\nimport argparse\nimport json\nimport subprocess\nimport sys\nimport os\nimport re\nfrom typing import Optional, List, Dict, Any, Tuple\n\n\nclass XiaodouyaController:\n    \"\"\"小豆芽应用控制器\"\"\"\n    \n    # 默认配置\n    DEFAULT_PATH = r\"C:\\Program Files\\xiaodouya\\新版小豆芽.exe\"\n    PROCESS_NAME = \"新版小豆芽.exe\"\n    \n    def __init__(self, json_output: bool = False):\n        self.json_output = json_output\n        self.powershell_path = self._find_powershell()\n        \n    def _find_powershell(self) -> str:\n        \"\"\"查找PowerShell路径\"\"\"\n        # WSL2常见路径\n        candidates = [\n            \"/mnt/c/Windows/System32/WindowsPowerShell/v1.0/powershell.exe\",\n            \"/mnt/c/Windows/System32/windowspowershell/v1.0/powershell.exe\",\n            \"/mnt/c/Windows/System32/powershell.exe\",\n        ]\n        \n        for path in candidates:\n            if os.path.exists(path):\n                return path\n        \n        # 尝试通过which查找\n        try:\n            result = subprocess.run(\n                [\"which\", \"powershell.exe\"],\n                capture_output=True,\n                text=True\n            )\n            if result.returncode == 0:\n                return result.stdout.strip()\n        except:\n            pass\n        \n        # 默认使用标准路径\n        return \"/mnt/c/Windows/System32/WindowsPowerShell/v1.0/powershell.exe\"\n    \n    def _encode_for_windows(self, text: str) -> bytes:\n        \"\"\"将文本编码为Windows可用的格式(GBK)\"\"\"\n        return text.encode('gbk', errors='replace')\n    \n    def _decode_from_windows(self, data: bytes) -> str:\n        \"\"\"从Windows解码数据(通常使用GBK)\"\"\"\n        # 尝试多种编码\n        for encoding in ['utf-8', 'gbk', 'gb2312', 'cp936', 'latin-1']:\n            try:\n                return data.decode(encoding)\n            except:\n                continue\n        # 最后尝试，忽略错误\n        return data.decode('utf-8', errors='replace')\n    \n    def _run_powershell(self, script: str) -> Tuple[bool, str]:\n        \"\"\"运行PowerShell脚本并返回结果\"\"\"\n        try:\n            # 使用参数传递脚本，避免命令行长度限制\n            result = subprocess.run(\n                [self.powershell_path, \"-NoProfile\", \"-ExecutionPolicy\", \"Bypass\", \"-Command\", script],\n                capture_output=True,\n                text=False  # 我们手动处理编码\n            )\n            \n            stdout = self._decode_from_windows(result.stdout)\n            stderr = self._decode_from_windows(result.stderr)\n            \n            if result.returncode != 0:\n                return False, f\"PowerShell error (code {result.returncode}): {stderr}\\n{stdout}\"\n            \n            return True, stdout\n            \n        except Exception as e:\n            return False, f\"Exception running PowerShell: {str(e)}\"\n    \n    def _output(self, data: Any, success: bool = True):\n        \"\"\"输出结果\"\"\"\n        if self.json_output:\n            output = {\n                \"success\": success,\n                \"data\": data if success else None,\n                \"error\": data if not success else None\n            }\n            print(json.dumps(output, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n        else:\n            if success:\n                if isinstance(data, (list, dict)):\n                    print(json.dumps(data, ensure_ascii=False, indent=2))\n                else:\n                    print(data)\n            else:\n                print(f\"Error: {data}\", file=sys.stderr)\n    \n    # ============ 核心功能实现 ============\n    \n    def find(self) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n        \"\"\"查找所有小豆芽进程\"\"\"\n        script = r\"\"\"\n# 查找小豆芽进程\n$processes = Get-Process | Where-Object { \n    $_.ProcessName -like \"*小豆芽*\" -or \n    $_.Name -like \"*xiaodouya*\" -or\n    $_.Path -like \"*xiaodouya*\"\n}\n\n# 如果上面的没找到，尝试查找新版小豆芽\nif (-not $processes) {\n    $processes = Get-Process | Where-Object { \n        $_.ProcessName -like \"*新版小豆芽*\" -or\n        $_.Name -like \"*新版小豆芽*\"\n    }\n}\n\n# 通用查找 - 检查窗口标题\nif (-not $processes) {\n    Add-Type @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\npublic class WindowFinder {\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool EnumWindows(EnumWindowsProc enumProc, IntPtr lParam);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern int GetWindowText(IntPtr hWnd, System.Text.StringBuilder lpString, int nMaxCount);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern uint GetWindowThreadProcessId(IntPtr hWnd, out uint lpdwProcessId);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool IsWindowVisible(IntPtr hWnd);\n    \n    public delegate bool EnumWindowsProc(IntPtr hWnd, IntPtr lParam);\n    \n    public static System.Collections.Generic.List<(int pid, string title)> FindWindows(string[] keywords) {\n        var results = new System.Collections.Generic.List<(int, string)>();\n        EnumWindows((hWnd, lParam) => {\n            if (!IsWindowVisible(hWnd)) return true;\n            var sb = new System.Text.StringBuilder(256);\n            GetWindowText(hWnd, sb, 256);\n            string title = sb.ToString();\n            uint pid = 0;\n            GetWindowThreadProcessId(hWnd, out pid);\n            foreach (var kw in keywords) {\n                if (title.ToLower().Contains(kw.ToLower())) {\n                    results.Add(((int)pid, title));\n                    break;\n                }\n            }\n            return true;\n        }, IntPtr.Zero);\n        return results;\n    }\n}\n\"@\n    $windows = [WindowFinder]::FindWindows(@(\"豆芽\", \"xiaodouya\", \"小豆芽\", \"新版小豆芽\"))\n    $uniquePids = $windows | Select-Object -Property pid -Unique | ForEach-Object { $_.pid }\n    $processes = Get-Process | Where-Object { $uniquePids -contains $_.Id }\n}\n\n# 输出结果\n$output = @()\nforeach ($proc in $processes) {\n    $mainWindowTitle = \"\"\n    try {\n        $mainWindowTitle = $proc.MainWindowTitle\n    } catch {}\n    \n    $path = \"\"\n    try {\n        $path = $proc.Path\n    } catch {}\n    \n    $output += @{\n        pid = $proc.Id\n        name = $proc.ProcessName\n        windowTitle = $mainWindowTitle\n        path = $path\n    }\n}\n\n$output | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 5\n\"\"\"\n        \n        success, output = self._run_powershell(script)\n        if not success:\n            # 尝试简单的查找方式\n            return self._find_simple()\n        \n        try:\n            data = json.loads(output)\n            # 确保返回列表\n            if isinstance(data, dict):\n                return [data]\n            return data if data else []\n        except:\n            return self._find_simple()\n    \n    def _find_simple(self) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n        \"\"\"简单的进程查找\"\"\"\n        script = r\"\"\"\nGet-Process | Where-Object { $_.ProcessName -like \"*豆芽*\" -or $_.ProcessName -like \"*xiaodouya*\" } | Select-Object Id, ProcessName, MainWindowTitle, Path | ConvertTo-Json -Depth 3\n\"\"\"\n        success, output = self._run_powershell(script)\n        if success:\n            try:\n                data = json.loads(output)\n                return [data] if isinstance(data, dict) else (data if data else [])\n            except:\n                pass\n        return []\n    \n    def activate(self, pid: int) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"激活指定PID的窗口到前台\"\"\"\n        script = fr\"\"\"\nAdd-Type @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\npublic class WindowActivator {{\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool SetForegroundWindow(IntPtr hWnd);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool ShowWindow(IntPtr hWnd, int nCmdShow);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool IsIconic(IntPtr hWnd);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern IntPtr GetForegroundWindow();\n    \n    public const int SW_RESTORE = 9;\n    public const int SW_SHOW = 5;\n    \n    public static bool ActivateWindow(IntPtr hWnd) {{\n        if (hWnd == IntPtr.Zero) return false;\n        \n        // 如果窗口最小化，恢复它\n        if (IsIconic(hWnd)) {{\n            ShowWindow(hWnd, SW_RESTORE);\n        }}\n        \n        // 强制设置前台窗口\n        return SetForegroundWindow(hWnd);\n    }}\n}}\n\"@\n\n$process = Get-Process -Id {pid} -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif (-not $process) {{\n    Write-Error \"Process with PID {pid} not found\"\n    exit 1\n}}\n\n$hwnd = $process.MainWindowHandle\nif ($hwnd -eq [IntPtr]::Zero) {{\n    # 尝试查找第一个可见窗口\n    Add-Type -TypeDefinition @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\nusing System.Text;\npublic class EnumWindowsHelper {{\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool EnumWindows(EnumWindowsProc enumProc, IntPtr lParam);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern int GetWindowText(IntPtr hWnd, StringBuilder lpString, int nMaxCount);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern uint GetWindowThreadProcessId(IntPtr hWnd, out uint lpdwProcessId);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool IsWindowVisible(IntPtr hWnd);\n    public delegate bool EnumWindowsProc(IntPtr hWnd, IntPtr lParam);\n    public static IntPtr FindWindowByPid(int pid) {{\n        IntPtr result = IntPtr.Zero;\n        EnumWindows((hWnd, lParam) => {{\n            if (!IsWindowVisible(hWnd)) return true;\n            uint wPid = 0;\n            GetWindowThreadProcessId(hWnd, out wPid);\n            if ((int)wPid == pid) {{\n                result = hWnd;\n                return false;\n            }}\n            return true;\n        }}, IntPtr.Zero);\n        return result;\n    }}\n}}\n\"@\n    $hwnd = [EnumWindowsHelper]::FindWindowByPid({pid})\n}}\n\nif ($hwnd -eq [IntPtr]::Zero) {{\n    Write-Error \"Could not find window for PID {pid}\"\n    exit 1\n}}\n\n$result = [WindowActivator]::ActivateWindow($hwnd)\nif ($result) {{\n    Write-Output '{{\"success\": true, \"message\": \"Window activated successfully\", \"hwnd\": \"' + $hwnd + '\"}}'\n}} else {{\n    Write-Error \"Failed to activate window\"\n    exit 1\n}}\n\"\"\"\n        \n        success, output = self._run_powershell(script)\n        if success:\n            try:\n                result = json.loads(output)\n                return result.get(\"success\", False)\n            except:\n                return True\n        return False\n    \n    def minimize(self, pid: int) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"最小化窗口\"\"\"\n        return self._show_window(pid, 6)  # SW_MINIMIZE = 6\n    \n    def maximize(self, pid: int) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"最大化窗口\"\"\"\n        return self._show_window(pid, 3)  # SW_MAXIMIZE = 3\n    \n    def _show_window(self, pid: int, cmd: int) -> bool:\n        \"\"\"执行窗口显示命令\"\"\"\n        script = fr\"\"\"\nAdd-Type @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\npublic class WindowController {{\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool ShowWindow(IntPtr hWnd, int nCmdShow);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool IsWindow(IntPtr hWnd);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern uint GetWindowThreadProcessId(IntPtr hWnd, out uint lpdwProcessId);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool EnumWindows(EnumWindowsProc enumProc, IntPtr lParam);\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool IsWindowVisible(IntPtr hWnd);\n    \n    public delegate bool EnumWindowsProc(IntPtr hWnd, IntPtr lParam);\n    \n    public static IntPtr FindWindowByPid(int pid) {{\n        IntPtr result = IntPtr.Zero;\n        EnumWindows((hWnd, lParam) => {{\n            uint wPid = 0;\n            GetWindowThreadProcessId(hWnd, out wPid);\n            if ((int)wPid == pid) {{\n                // 优先选择可见窗口\n                if (IsWindowVisible(hWnd) || result == IntPtr.Zero) {{\n                    result = hWnd;\n                    if (IsWindowVisible(hWnd)) return false;\n                }}\n            }}\n            return true;\n        }}, IntPtr.Zero);\n        return result;\n    }}\n}}\n\"@\n\n$process = Get-Process -Id {pid} -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue\nif (-not $process) {{\n    Write-Error \"Process with PID {pid} not found\"\n    exit 1\n}}\n\n$hwnd = [WindowController]::FindWindowByPid({pid})\nif ($hwnd -eq [IntPtr]::Zero) {{\n    Write-Error \"Could not find window for PID {pid}\"\n    exit 1\n}}\n\n$result = [WindowController]::ShowWindow($hwnd, {cmd})\nWrite-Output '{{\"success\": true, \"result\": ' + $result.ToString().ToLower() + '}}'\n\"\"\"\n        \n        success, output = self._run_powershell(script)\n        if success:\n            try:\n                result = json.loads(output)\n                return result.get(\"success\", False)\n            except:\n                return True\n        return False\n    \n    def list_controls(self, pid: int) -> List[Dict[str, Any]]:\n        \"\"\"列出窗口中的所有UI控件\"\"\"\n        script = fr\"\"\"\nAdd-Type @\"\nusing System;\nusing System.Collections.Generic;\nusing System.Runtime.InteropServices;\nusing System.Text;\nusing System.Windows.Automation;\n\npublic class UIAutomationHelper {{\n    // Win32 API\n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern uint GetWindowThreadProcessId(IntPtr hWnd, out uint lpdwProcessId);\n    \n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool EnumWindows(EnumWindowsProc enumProc, IntPtr lParam);\n    \n    [DllImport(\"user32.dll\")]\n    public static extern bool IsWindowVisible(IntPtr hWnd);\n    \n    public delegate bool EnumWindowsProc(IntPtr hWnd, IntPtr lParam);\n    \n    public static IntPtr FindWindowByPid(int pid) {{\n        IntPtr result = IntPtr.Zero;\n        EnumWindows((hWnd, lParam) => {{\n            uint wPid = 0;\n            GetWindowThreadProcessId(hWnd, out wPid);\n            if ((int)wPid == pid) {{\n                if (IsWindowVisible(hWnd) || result == IntPtr.Zero) {{\n                    result = hWnd;\n                    if (IsWindowVisible(hWnd)) return false;\n                }}\n            }}\n            return true;"}},{"type":"text","text":"n"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"volcengine-plan","model":"kimi-k2.5","usage":{"input":11762,"output":4197,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":15959,"cost":{"input":0.0000011762,"output":8.394000000000001e-7,"cacheRead":0,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0000020156000000000002}},"stopReason":"length","timestamp":1772173796365}}
